data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath raised ranch in the heart of Ulster County on 1.1 acres! Bay window in living room illuminates the 1st floor with natural light. Large kitchen with lots of cabinet & counter space. Spacious bedrooms. Family room & den on lower level. Plenty of room inside and out for family gatherings and entertaining. Close to 9W, I-84,Stewart Airport, NYS Thruway, shopping, schools and amenities.  Sold as-is. Buyer to pay NYS and any local transfer taxes. Offers with financing must be accompanied by pre- qual letter; cash offers with proof of funds. **Please see agent remarks for access, showing instructions and offer presentation remarks.**  Buyer to pay NYS and any local transfer taxes.
